    "gp_section_615206760433451824": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "9ac00d7b2ec1a19a819e27f0bd20ac4d8aa3458b9fddb855890f27d9aace254b_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg0vIH7rl9L_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/1_ad79ef62-7588-43be-a10a-5826ab3ce162.webp",
        "gg1UonB-KIb_altLeft": "Describes the appearance of the image",
        "gg1UonB-KIb_altRight": "Describes the appearance of the image",
        "gg1UonB-KIb_imageLeft_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/2_1.webp",
        "gg1UonB-KIb_imageRight_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/2_2.webp",
        "gg1UonB-KIb_leftImageLabel": "Before",
        "gg1UonB-KIb_rightImageLabel": "After",
        "gg1UonB-KIb_titleLeft": "Title",
        "gg1UonB-KIb_titleRight": "Title",
        "gg2I6wHUPsE_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">My dad - 57, recently divorced, newly single for the first time in decades - standing shoulder to shoulder with his Italian first cousins. Men who shared his exact bloodline on my grandfather's side.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The Italian men looked a decade younger. Not surgery different. Just sharp.&nbsp;</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Jawlines still defined. Necks still tight. Men in their 60s who could pass for their late 40s, standing next to my dad who looked every single year of his age. Maybe more.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Same bloodline. Same genetics on my grandfather's side. The only difference was where they'd lived and what they'd been putting on their skin for the last 30 years.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">My dad noticed it too. Said nothing. But I saw him clocking it.</span></p>",
        "gg2pcKyK_RB_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">My dad's skin had already started changing from a basic farmacia cream. But those creams were built for Italian men who'd been using them since their twenties. My dad was 57 and starting from zero. He didn't have decades to catch up.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">He needed something that used the olive oil as a carrier - the thing that actually got through the door - but packed it with ingredients that could turn the collagen signal back on fast. Not over years. Over months.</span><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Nothing like that existed. Not in Italy. Not in America. Not anywhere.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">So I decided to build it.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">I found a three-generation olive farm twenty minutes from where I was staying - the specific cold-pressed variety from this region was non-negotiable.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Then a family-owned pharmaceutical lab that's been formulating for men's skin since 1987. Two independent cosmetic scientists validated every concentration.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">After lots of negotiating (and lots of $$$). We got to work.</span></p>",
        "gg34wKBKtor_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The morning after the wedding I walked into the local farmacia. The kind of place where the woman behind the counter has been working there for 50 years and knows every man in town by name.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>I asked her one question: \"what do most men here use on their skin?\"</strong></span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">She didn't hesitate. Pointed to a low shelf near the back wall. Four or five creams in plain packaging, restocked quietly for decades.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Every single one had cold-pressed Italian olive oil near the top of the ingredient list. The same stuff you cook with. I almost laughed. But the pharmacist wasn't joking - and neither were the faces of every man over 60 in that town.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">I bought the top one and handed it to my dad that night. He rolled his eyes, but he'd run out of arguments - he'd already tried everything else back home.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">He started using them that night. Twenty seconds before bed. Nothing complicated.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Within a few weeks something was actually shifting. Nothing dramatic. But real. His skin looked less tired. The heaviness around his jaw had softened. He looked like a man who'd slept well rather than a man who hadn't slept properly in two years.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">But the Italian men around me had been using this stuff their entire lives. My dad didn't have decades, there was no point in him being wrinkle free at 90 years old. He needed something that worked in months, not years.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">I went back to my room and started reading.</span></p>",
        "gg5MFHFn_c-_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">7. My Dad's 90-Day Transformation</span></p>",
        "gg7YaIS1Fct_text": "<p>Week 12:</p>",
        "gg8Dp5QrHKP_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">You can close this page and nothing changes. Same mirror tomorrow morning. Same face. Same feeling.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;\">Or you can do what my dad did. Twenty seconds. Before bed. And see what happens in 60 days.</span></p>",
        "gg9ncGWbQlb_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">10. 20 Seconds Before Bed, That's It.</span></p>",
        "ggBZ4h-EbFb_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">My dad is not a skincare guy. Never has been. He'd sooner rewire the garage than stand in front of a mirror with a jar of cream. But the last couple of years had gotten to him - the jaw going soft, the neck loosening, looking tired no matter how much he slept.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">So he'd quietly tried a few things. The way men do. Without telling anyone.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Drugstore moisturisers - months of nothing. Retinol from a pharmacy - face went red and raw for two weeks, looked worse than when he started, never touched it again. Tallow? Moisturized pretty well but his face looked the exact same months later. Even looked into Botox. Couldn't stomach paying every three months forever just to maintain.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Nothing had moved the needle.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">He'd stopped trying by the time we got to Italy. Not because he didn't care - because he'd tried enough to believe that nothing actually worked.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">I was starting to think he was right.</span></p>",
        "ggDacs4WIog_text": "<p>Weeks 1-2:</p>",
        "ggE1W1Hv6pp_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The neck and the jawline. This was the big one. The turkey neck that had started this whole thing - the reason I walked into that farmacia the morning after the wedding - was visibly tighter. The jawline that had been slowly melting into his neck for half a decade had an edge again. Not twenty years younger. A convincing ten. The kind of difference that makes people ask questions rather than pay compliments.</span></p>",
        "ggGOr1-z7mt_altLeft": "Describes the appearance of the image",
        "ggGOr1-z7mt_altRight": "Describes the appearance of the image",
        "ggGOr1-z7mt_imageLeft_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/3_1.webp",
        "ggGOr1-z7mt_imageRight_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/3_2.webp",
        "ggGOr1-z7mt_leftImageLabel": "Before",
        "ggGOr1-z7mt_rightImageLabel": "After",
        "ggGOr1-z7mt_titleLeft": "Title",
        "ggGOr1-z7mt_titleRight": "Title",
        "ggHFd1NVbpq_text": "<p>Week 8:</p>",
        "ggHO-I3s8Kk_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">Here's what I think happens over the next 60 days:</span></p>",
        "ggHppWLzMjm_text": "<p><strong>Weeks 1-2</strong>, your skin feels different. Tighter. Less heavy. Nothing dramatic, but something shifts.</p>",
        "ggItKg_SdwC_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">We couldn't launch in the US straight away. So we started local. A small first batch. My dad. A few men in the town where the lab was based.</span></p>",
        "ggJXrlmiPm5_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">5. One Farm. One Lab. Eighteen Months to Get It Right.</span></p>",
        "ggMJpIqNYzV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/w2.webp",
        "ggNIdsNjXP5_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/6_c43fc91b-71c2-45e2-88c5-9aad77c47ca0.webp",
        "ggNrKRvPt0v_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/8_947728cc-93c3-48db-87de-e2247a737315.webp",
        "ggQK_Fv6ygd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/ww2.webp",
        "ggQQA_ynkXB_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/ww3.webp",
        "ggTCyXKh_Rk_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/7_aaaa3929-cbae-4bc7-bed1-40d23bbb5a0d.webp",
        "ggUG5Fdg3dy_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">6. Why This Works for Men Over 45 When Others Don't</span></p>",
        "ggUernq8rvJ_text": "<p><strong>Week 4</strong>, the eyes change. The puffiness softens. You look less tired without changing your sleep.</p>",
        "ggUiJzKVWK7_altLeft": "Describes the appearance of the image",
        "ggUiJzKVWK7_altRight": "Describes the appearance of the image",
        "ggUiJzKVWK7_imageLeft_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/1_1.webp",
        "ggUiJzKVWK7_imageRight_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/1_2.webp",
        "ggUiJzKVWK7_leftImageLabel": "Before",
        "ggUiJzKVWK7_rightImageLabel": "After",
        "ggUiJzKVWK7_titleLeft": "Title",
        "ggUiJzKVWK7_titleRight": "Title",
        "ggUzNRL519Y_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/h.webp",
        "ggVBMxxJteA_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">1. That's what I was staring at during my cousin's wedding in Italy last summer.</span></p>",
        "ggW6FbYxv8I_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/w3.webp",
        "ggWvY_WCyvN_text": "<p>This is the part where you decide.</p>",
        "ggXYv5KXZAa_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Gianluca, 64</strong>, had never put anything on his face in his life. Not even the farmacia creams. His brother talked him into trying it. Forty-five days later his undereye bags kind of evaporated.</span></p>",
        "ggY9HBZKKCB_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">That's when the eyes changed. The puffiness that had been sitting under his eyes for years - the kind that made him look exhausted even on a Saturday morning - started pulling back. Not gone. But softened. Like someone had taken an eraser to the worst of it.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">He FaceTimed me and I noticed before he said anything.</span></p>",
        "ggZkJhJaDYL_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/ww3.webp",
        "ggaA6qbkBb6_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Every cream my dad tried - every moisturiser, every retinol, every tallow balm - failed for the same reason. They couldn't get through. The skin barrier in men over 45 is thicker, drier, and more resistant than any skincare brand wants to admit. So the active ingredients just sat on the surface and evaporated by morning.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">But this? The base is cold-pressed Italian olive oil from that single family farm down the road. The delivery system. Its lipid structure mirrors the skin's own fats so closely that it bypasses the barrier entirely - carrying everything else straight to the dermal layer where collagen is actually built.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">No other oil does this. Not coconut. Not tallow. Not the synthetic delivery vehicles American brands use that trigger inflammation on the way through.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The signal is retinyl palmitate, AKA \"The Gentleman's Retinol\". Clinically proven to trigger the same collagen-rebuilding response as prescription retinol - but through a slow enzymatic conversion that only activates once it's already inside the skin.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">No inflammation. No barrier damage. No two-week disaster phase.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The anchor is sodium hyaluronate. Molecules small enough to bypass the surface entirely and lock hydration at the collagen layer - exactly where new collagen is forming. Not sitting on top where it evaporates by morning.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The olive oil carries it through. The retinyl palmitate sends the signal. The sodium hyaluronate holds everything in place while the rebuilding happens.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The first jar went to my dad.</span></p>",
        "ggamSuHJC6l_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">9. America, Finally.</span></p>",
        "ggasS4e-kFz_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/9_e5088413-adca-43c8-8b13-157edd3f1e0b.webp",
        "ggcce8AoybY_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/3_ecd241eb-86c3-4108-a30f-c8c97e5557dd.webp",
        "ggcyJQiQwnL_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">3. The Pharmacy Visit That Explained Why American Solutions Don't Work.</span></p>",
        "ggdsuyRtxNy_text": "<p><strong>Week 4</strong>, the eyes change. The puffiness softens. You look less tired without changing your sleep.</p>",
        "ggeVU7pWJ4l_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/5_1ce16221-e5cc-40dd-b838-5f9eca753f12.webp",
        "ggfR4GMsVHS_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">8. We Launched in Italy First...</span></p>",
        "ggg4053Jf9x_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;font-size:14px;\">No dramatic transformation. Nothing he could point to in a photo. But something was shifting underneath. His skin looked less tired. Less heavy. Like a guy who'd finally gotten a full night's sleep after two years of not sleeping properly.</span></p>",
        "gggUz4lYPgq_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/4_85e78db8-46e6-43ba-84d0-b4023429c189.webp",
        "gggb95LF2Ty_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">That's what happened to my dad. To Enzo. To Marco. To the 70,000 Italian men who've been using this every night.</span></p>",
        "ggi8SksHtLw_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">SerlinoLab is a single cream. Not a system. Not a five-step routine. Not something that requires you to watch a tutorial or rearrange your bathroom cabinet. You wash your face, you put it on, you go to bed.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The olive oil carries everything through. The retinyl palmitate sends the collagen signal. The sodium hyaluronate locks it in place while the rebuilding happens. Three ingredients, each one useless without the other two, each one at full therapeutic concentration from a pharmaceutical lab that's been doing this since 1987.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">One jar lasts a full month. It costs less than a single Botox consultation. Less than the retinol that burned your face. Less than the drawer full of moisturisers that didn't do anything.</span></p>",
        "ggju41sWagd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/ww2.webp",
        "ggkksSNtBTy_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">That's how it spread.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Within twelve months SerlinoLab had gone from a test batch in one town to the number one best-selling men's anti-aging cream in the country. 70,000+ Italian men using it daily. 20 Seconds before bed.</span><br>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggkuMxDja1E_text": "<p><strong>Week 8</strong>, the neck and jawline tighten. The loose skin pulls back. You simply stop thinking about it. Not because you gave up. Because there's nothing to think about anymore. You look like you again.</p>",
        "ggmAMWkhoBI_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/ww1.webp",
        "ggnuBOyFH4w_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/w4.webp",
        "ggpR1lH9si6_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/ww1.webp",
        "ggpTTzQjFwo_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/2_1e374bf4-8ed7-40eb-bbeb-d738713a0bf0.webp",
        "ggpgIVN_po9_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">This is him now. That's the photo he sent me. No filter. No special lighting. Just my dad looking like my dad again.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Oh, and he mentioned he's been out on a few dates since.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:transparent;color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">That was enough. Now I needed to know if it worked for everyone else.</span></p>",
        "ggqhm6q2tVN_text": "<p><strong>Weeks 1-2</strong>, your skin feels different. Tighter. Less heavy. Nothing dramatic, but something shifts.</p>",
        "ggqtiqo6Vdk_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Use every drop for 60 days. Follow the routine - twenty seconds before bed, nothing else. If you don't see a real, visible difference when you look in the mirror, I'll give you every penny back. No forms. No phone calls. No questions. Just your money back.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">I can make that guarantee because I watched it work on the man I care about most. And because 70,000 men have proven it wasn't a fluke.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Here's the only catch:</strong></span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The olive oil comes from one farm. Three generations, same family, same cold-pressed process. One harvest per year. When it's gone, it's gone. The lab runs the way it's run since 1987 and I'm not asking them to change that.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">We've sold out after every restock. I can't tell you when the next batch will be ready once this one goes.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">If the button below is still active, the current batch hasn't sold out yet.</span></p>",
        "ggqx_HQJTxr_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">2. Drugstore Creams. Retinol. Tallow. Even Botox. Nothing Worked.</span></p>",
        "ggrE5XxbWL9_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Marco, 57,</strong> had worked construction his whole life. Thirty years of sun and wind, never once thinking about his skin. Six weeks in and the deep lines started softening. Eight weeks and his daughter saw a photo and asked what was different. He hadn't told anyone he was using it.</span></p>",
        "ggsjRy3ajEc_text": "<p>Week 4:</p>",
        "ggtRfRCvoUr_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\"><strong>Enzo, 62</strong>, ran the hardware shop two streets from the lab. He'd used the same farmacia cream for fifteen years. Three weeks on ours and his wife asked what he'd done differently. She noticed the neck first - said it looked like it did when they got married.</span></p>",
        "ggt_YuiuoS6_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0871/6681/2407/files/w1.webp",
        "ggti1isokfe_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">11. Your 60-Day \"Mirror Guarantee\"</span></p>",
        "ggvgfRYO_wS_text": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;\">4. \"Dermal Drag\" - The Hidden Reason Men's Faces Collapse After 45.</span></p>",
        "ggwSveoeQNZ_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">January this year, the US approval finally came through. After eighteen months of building this thing in a small Italian town, I had no idea if American men would even care.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">We put up one Instagram post. Sent one email to a small list. Nothing else.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">It sold out in minutes.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">I remember staring at my phone watching the orders come in and thinking there must be a glitch. There wasn't. Men had been waiting for something that actually worked - they just didn't know it existed yet.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">We've restocked three times since then. Sold out every time. The problem is simple - the olive oil comes from one farm, one harvest per year. The lab has been making products the same way since 1987 and I'm not going to ask a family-run operation to cut corners because demand spiked.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">So when a batch is gone, it's gone. And I can't tell you when the next one will be ready.</span></p>",
        "ggyPTrSb9KK_text": "<p><strong>Week 8</strong>, the neck and jawline tighten. The loose skin pulls back. You simply stop thinking about it. Not because you gave up. Because there's nothing to think about anymore. You look like you again.</p>",
        "ggzOMQ7aNPp_text": "<p><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The lipid structure of cold-pressed Italian olive oil is almost identical to the natural fats in male skin. The skin doesn't treat it as a foreign substance - it recognises it, opens up, and lets it through. Every American product my dad tried was knocking on a door that was never going to open. The olive oil walked straight in.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">That explained the delivery. But I needed to understand why men's skin collapses after 45 in the first place.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">Researchers call it <strong>\"Dermal Drag\"</strong> - the slow, progressive loss of structural collagen that causes the jawline to soften, the neck to loosen, and the face to take on that heavy tired look that no amount of sleep fixes. By the time most men notice it in the mirror, it's already been happening for years.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The problem isn't that the skin forgets how to rebuild collagen. It stops receiving the instruction to do so. The signal goes quiet. And without something delivering that signal to the right layer, nothing you put on your face will ever change that.</span></p><p><br><span style=\"background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);color:#17162E;font-size:11pt;\">The olive oil could get through the door. I needed to find ingredients that turned the collagen signal back 'on'...</span></p>",
        "ggzSxlyVqRg_label": "<p><span style=\"color:#17162E;font-size:px;\">Try Risk-Free</span></p>"
      },
